data.description: Escape the constraints of an HOA with this unique opportunity! Embrace the allure of rural living as you explore the potential of a home currently undergoing construction in the serene countryside of Lancaster County. This property offers a harmonious mix of rustic tranquility and contemporary comfort. Seize the moment to be a part of this thrilling journey and transform this under-construction dwelling into your very own rural sanctuary. Don't miss out on creating a haven that perfectly balances the charm of country living with the conveniences of modern life. Approximate completion timeframe is mid-December.
